description: Glen Eagle Resources Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, development, and evaluation of mining properties. The company holds a 100% interest in the Moose Lake phosphate property located in St-Jean Lake area, Quebec; and 80% interest in Piedra Dorada mining concession located in the mining district of El Corpus in Honduras. It is also involved in the recovery of gold and silver from tailings; and recovery of gold from rocks. Glen Eagle Resources Inc. is headquartered in Saint-Lambert, Canada.
